Skoro nic si nesnědla.

973
00:52:02,550 --> 00:52:03,410
Ale, ne.

974
00:52:03,410 --> 00:52:05,470
Nic se neděje. Pojďme jíst.

975
00:52:08,720 --> 00:52:10,070
Zítra večer...

976
00:52:10,070 --> 00:52:12,770
